@managerId = {{createManager.response.body.$.id}}

### Criar uma nova empresa
// @name createCompany
POST {{baseUrl}}/company
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Empresa Exemplo",
  "cnpj": "12345678000100",
  "managerId": "{{managerId}}"
}
###

@companyId = {{createCompany.response.body.id}}

### Buscar uma empresa por ID
GET  {{baseUrl}}/company/{{companyId}}

### Listar todas as empresas
GET  {{baseUrl}}/company

### Atualizar uma empresa
PUT  {{baseUrl}}/company/{{companyId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Empresa Atualizada",
  "cnpj": "98765432000100",
  "manager": {
    "name": "Maria Oliveira",
    "email": "maria.oliveira@example.com",
    "phone": "11988888888",
    "cpf": "98765432100"
  }
}

### Deletar uma empresa
DELETE  {{baseUrl}}/company/{{companyId}}

